00:43:18,071 --> 00:43:22,615
And for, if there's any managers here, it's also a great way to make your people work nights.

676
00:43:24,037 --> 00:43:25,959
But, yeah, I definitely do that.

677
00:43:27,064 --> 00:43:32,370
Then, you know, giving your players some agency, some stake in the development of the game is great.

678
00:43:32,930 --> 00:43:34,812
A lot of people are running focus groups.

679
00:43:34,852 --> 00:43:36,714
We have a democratically elected focus group.

680
00:43:36,734 --> 00:43:39,017
That doesn't maybe, you know, maybe that doesn't work for everybody.

681
00:43:40,029 --> 00:43:43,171
Maybe we'll have the People's Council of Krust can't be one day.

682
00:43:43,812 --> 00:43:48,495
Or if people just want to do more casual focus groups that they handpick,

683
00:43:48,715 --> 00:43:54,679
there's still things you can probably do like allowing players to vote on certain priorities

684
00:43:54,779 --> 00:44:00,102
or final outcomes or stuff like that on certain things in whatever limited capacity you're comfortable with.

685
00:44:00,182 --> 00:44:02,163
But it's fun to give your players a say.

686
00:44:04,332 --> 00:44:08,856
And then maintaining direct, ungated communication is something that I recommend.

687
00:44:09,216 --> 00:44:13,020
It's not for everyone, I know that, and there's a lot of companies that are very big,

688
00:44:13,040 --> 00:44:15,463
where things have to be more formal and I completely understand that.

689
00:44:17,178 --> 00:44:20,140
But I would definitely recommend checking it out.

690
00:44:20,280 --> 00:44:24,022
One good thing about it is that we see who's good at communicating

691
00:44:24,342 --> 00:44:28,163
and then we can, for example, decide to send those people to those player gatherings I talked about.

692
00:44:28,183 --> 00:44:32,845
So by spending some extra time on engaging with the community and building a relationship there,

693
00:44:32,885 --> 00:44:35,247
you might end up in Australia one day talking about EVE.

694
00:44:36,389 --> 00:44:41,712
And like I said, if you have a chance to go the formal route or the more playful, ungated route of communication,

695
00:44:41,752 --> 00:44:48,216
I'd recommend the more playful one, because we are in the entertainment business and we sometimes forget that.

