00:52:51,875 --> 00:52:52,516
we air all of it.

819
00:52:52,957 --> 00:52:53,778
We could do that.

820
00:52:54,579 --> 00:52:56,302
But yeah, we haven't had a lot of follow up.

821
00:52:56,322 --> 00:52:59,608
But we'll have to see if that comes up.

